data.description: Gorgeous equestrian sanctuary in peaceful Cottage Lake Bridle Estates. Stately brick entrance welcomes you to warm & inviting fully updated home on 2+pastoral acres. Main floor~beautiful hand scraped hardwoods, spacious chefs kitchen w/quartz counters, SS appliances, charming sunroom/dining nook, formal living/dining. Oversize rec room w/separate entry~office/media room/MIL. Upper level w/office nook, full bath, 4 bedrooms including primary en-suite w/stunning new bathroom. Equine components~4 stall barn w/paddocks, 130x60 outdoor arena, pastures. Deck w/hot tub, patio, fire pit, darling playhouse. A/C, 3 car garage +EV charger, RV/trailer parking. Enjoy country living close to Woodinville, wineries, quick access to 522. Northshore Schools.
